    <h1 class="section-title">Wellness &amp; Benefits of Running</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Few things give so much for so little. Running isn't just exercise — it's a way to care for
      your body and mind at the same time. A few kilometres are enough to reduce stress, boost your
      immune system and make you feel stronger inside and out.
    </p>

