        </div>
        <h3>Brain</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Better focus</li>
          <li>Less anxiety</li>
          <li>Better mood</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="card-source" href="https://www.health.harvard.edu/blog/how-simply-moving-benefits-your-mental-health-201603289350" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source: Harvard Health ↗</a><br>
        <a class="card-link" href="post-trexsimo-imikranies-en.html">How running helps the brain →</a>
