          <div class="card-stat"><span class="num">↑</span><span class="cap">aerobic endurance</span></div>
        </div>
        <h3>Lungs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Better endurance</li>
          <li>Increased oxygenation</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="card-source" href="https://lunghealth.ca/fitness-influences-lung-capacity-overall-health/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source: Lung Health Foundation ↗</a><br>
