    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:4rem;">What you gain after...</h2>
    <p class="lead">The benefits of running build up gradually. Here's what changes over time.</p>
    <p class="lead" style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:-0.6rem;">Tap a card to see why it happens.</p>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <button class="timeline-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <div class="timeline-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 12h4l3 8 4-16 3 8h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>1 run</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Better mood</li>
            <li>Endorphin release</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="timeline-chevron"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="timeline-more"><p>Why? Your body releases endorphins and dopamine within minutes of exercise — which is why you feel better almost right away.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <button class="timeline-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <div class="timeline-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4"/><path d="M8 2v4"/><path d="M3 10h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>1 month</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Better fitness level</li>
            <li>Less fatigue</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="timeline-chevron"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="timeline-more"><p>Why? Your heart and lungs start adapting to the extra load, so the same distance starts to feel easier.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <button class="timeline-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <div class="timeline-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4"/><path d="M8 2v4"/><path d="M3 10h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>6 months</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Better cardiorespiratory endurance</li>
            <li>Lower resting heart rate</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="timeline-chevron"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="timeline-more"><p>Why? You build more capillaries and your heart pumps a greater volume of blood with every beat.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <button class="timeline-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <div class="timeline-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4"/><path d="M8 2v4"/><path d="M3 10h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>1 year</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Significant health improvement</li>
            <li>Greater self-confidence</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="timeline-chevron"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="timeline-more"><p>Why? These changes become a lasting habit — running now supports you instead of wearing you down.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:4rem;">Did you know?</h2>
    <div class="fact-grid">
      <div class="fact-card">
        <p class="fact-label"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="6"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><path d="M10 21h4"/></svg> Did you know?</p>
        <p>20 minutes of running can instantly improve your mood.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <p class="fact-label"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="6"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><path d="M10 21h4"/></svg> Did you know?</p>
        <p>Regular exercise can lower your resting heart rate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <p class="fact-label"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="6"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><path d="M10 21h4"/></svg> Did you know?</p>
        <p>A few weeks of consistent running is enough to boost your immune system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:4rem;">Small habits, big difference</h2>
    <ul class="tips">
      <li>
        <strong>Sleep = training</strong>
        Your body grows stronger while it rests, not while it runs. 7–8 hours of sleep make the difference.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Hydrate before you're thirsty</strong>
        Drink water throughout the day, not just around your run.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Warm-up &amp; stretching</strong>
        Five minutes before and after reduce injuries and help recovery.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <section class="final-cta">
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready to start?</h2>
      <p>You don't need to run fast. Just take your first step today.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a class="btn" href="programma-5k-en.html">See the 5K plan</a>
        <a class="btn-alt" href="post-arxarios-trexsimo-en.html">Beginner's guide</a>
